text: Ordered hot plate chicken set at $6.50. Giving a 3 star as there are improvement areas - rice is undercooked and hot plate chicken was generally bland. Although miso soup was well balanced and services were generous.
Very poor service and attitude. Maybe the staff hasn't get her pay yet. Stop giving your customers LCLY face! ! They don't owe you anything...
